Based on Katniss' behavior in Mockingjay, she would have done the same had she not had so many people working to keep her alive.
During her imprisonment, Katniss thinks she is completely isolated and alone despite the fact that there are so many people continuously supporting her.
She feels abandoned by all of her loved ones and alienated by the government she had once placed her trust in.
